{"type":"article_comment","id":310152,"parentType":"article","parentId":16484,"uid":25065,"contents":"<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/item_id-309515#answer_list_309515\"><blockquote>地各有其财 而货币统一 不然各邦流通颇为苦恼 </blockquote></a><br>\n食貨原理，幣者，財也。製其幣者制其財。強一其幣，歐盟之厄。為苦不以殊幣，以暴府禁幣出入。","date":"2020-03-22","agreeCount":0,"discussionCount":0}